{"TopicId":142755,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Kerbals Stuck Boarding after fairing deployment.","CreatedByName":"Zamite","CreatedById":121717,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T11:58:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Zamite","CreatedById":121717,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T11:58:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EKSP Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0v1.1.3.1289 (Windows x64)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EWhat Happens:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0After deploying an Airstream Protective Shell if a Kerbal goes on EVA it will be stuck when boarding. Can\u0027t switch to the stuck kerbal but can control the ship, but the crew.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EMods / Add-Ons:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EAll Stock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003ESteps to Replicate:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n1. Create a vehicle composed of a Command pod (I tried both the Mk1 and Mk1-2) and an Airstream protective Shell (tried the 1.25 and 2.5 respectively).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Launch vehicle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Deploy fairing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. EVA and Board.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappens every single time on a clean install and new sandbox save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EResult:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EKerbal gets stuck while boarding, and you can\u0027t control him again. Since he is on the ladder you can\u0027t move to Space Center without losing progress.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EFixes/Workarounds:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(251,251,251);\u0022\u003E\n- If you go to Space center and come back to ship (reloading the ship)\u00A0after deploying the fairing the bug will not happen anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T21:54:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can confirm this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery annoying bug.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve pretty much stopped using fairings atm because of this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zamite","CreatedById":121717,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-29T22:06:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI still use them, I just have to remember to use the workaround.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-30T11:42:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry quicksaving then quickloading, it will be quicker than returning to the vessel from the tracking station.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Slaghead","CreatedById":150721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-07T22:11:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAhhhhh! \u00A0So it\u0027s the fairing causing this. \u00A0Well, I\u0027m not going to stop using fairings but it makes sense because I\u0027ve done a lot of EVA\u0027s without issue before I unlocked fairings without issue. \u00A0But this issue has been happening recently and I think all of those ships had fairings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"avalancha","CreatedById":143355,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T20:28:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStarted up Keepass and logged in just to upvote this thread! Thanks for confirming I\u0027m not going crazy here. Can confirm this, very annoying\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-01T21:50:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222700532\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142755\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470083284\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022143355\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022avalancha\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, avalancha said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStarted up Keepass and logged in just to upvote this thread! Thanks for confirming I\u0027m not going crazy here. Can confirm this, very annoying\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/87737-ksp-v113-stock-bug-fix-modules-release-v113b1-10-jul-16/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003EUpdate 1.1.3a.1:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:22.4px;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003EDeprecated several modules (that have been incorporated into stock)\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003EAdded a small fix for non-responsive kerbal EVA lights\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(128,0,0);\u0022\u003EAdded fix for fairings that was causing kerbals to get stuck on EVA and docking ports to break (becoming perma-stuck).\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"}]}